body:
David Tennant Podcast on Instagram: “#davidtennantdoesapodcastwith #gordonbrown #tuesday #podcast #comingsoon #davidtennant #ukpolitics”

I love many things in David, but he’s respect for others is one of my favorite traits. You could hear his admiration for Ian and now again, he is respectful and just so… Well mannered? Idk, it shoul be normal for people to be well behaved etc., yet it is not so common unfortunately. And I am super happy that David is such a good person, with very nice manners

blog.name: ygrain-synaerasis
blog.title: L'Echappée Belle d' Ygraïn
blog.description:
" Elle voulait une vie d'aventures, une vie folle, une vie plus grande qu'elle.Et l'on disait tout autour d'elle : [Ygraïn] rêve". Timothée de Fombelle, Victoria rêve

Je ne sais pas dessiner, les artworks que vous verrez ici ne sont pas les miens. Mais vous trouverez toujours un lien vers une gallerie de leurs auteurs. Personnellement, je ne fais que des montages (wallpaper, digiscrap, bannière ...) à partir de captures d'écran (screencap).. Ce tumblr est ma gallerie de rêves éphémères, mon échappée belle où je viens me ressourcer, me changer les idées, trouver un support à mes rêveries grâce aux fabuleux arts de d'autres artistes. .
Pour me contacter, en cas de problème: ygrain@gmail.com

Sinon: mon blog de lecture est: https://les-lectures-d-ygrain.tumblr.com/

summary: I am *SO* not a scary movie person, but I was completely sucked in by this film. The performances were excellent, especially...
body:
PSA: Go watch Bad Samaritan on Prime Video.

I am *SO* not a scary movie person, but I was completely sucked in by this film. The performances were excellent, especially Robert Sheehan, who I have never seen in a role quite this serious. I’m used to him being the silly, snarky asshole with a heart of gold a la Misfits or The Umbrella Academy (my love for Nathan and Klaus is next level right now), so I wasn’t sure how he would be minus the wisecracks.

CAN I JUST SAY: He was on point, my dudes.

Bonus: Cute Irish accent intact.

That is the face of a man whose life is rapidly unraveling. 🥺

I won’t post any David Tennant photos here, because his every facial expression left me profoundly troubled in this movie. HOW does he look so creepy?? My Tenth Doctor?? Acting skills, impressive. Still love you, but also please don’t come near me. 🥶

Fellow chickens, have a blankie close and buckle up for this one. I have to admit the trailer didn’t wow me when I saw it last year, but I am so glad I took a chance on this one.

👍🏻👍🏻
